ked interest bearing and index linked financial instruments have had, in the last 10 years, the index changed from (1) RPI to CPI, and (2) CPI to RPI; and what the rationale was for those changes.","false","Biography information for Lord Sharkey",,"Lord Sharkey","HL13609"
